\"Ezra.3.12\" class=\"v15_3_12\">12</sup>But many of the priests and Levites and heads of fathers\u2019 houses, old men who had seen the first house, wept with a loud voice when they saw the foundation of this house being laid, though many shouted aloud for joy, </span><span class=\"v15_3_13\"><sup id=\"Ezra.3.13\" class=\"v15_3_13\">13</sup>so that the people could not distinguish the sound of the joyful shout from the sound of the people\u2019s weeping, for the people shouted with a great shout, and the sound was heard far away.</span></p>\n</div>\n", 
